{
  "stem": "20088.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A selection, when my mother was selected to the wrong side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So about 20 or 30 people were put to the wrong side, and they were standing there naked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we were all naked, and we were still standing there, and they were marched out to a different direction from where we were going.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, well, I've lost my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I ran to my mother, my mother still whispered to me, go and tell Mini.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we were moved at night to a different part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I said, you know, they were all small areas, always separate barbed wire, but with a gate on the outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, we were in sort of a double camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one camp, A camp and B camp, and that was separated by gates with barbed wired and sentries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this had happened in A camp, and we were marched in the night to B camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I know Mini was in A Camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- and I thought, well, I have to go and tell Mini.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so in the middle of the night, I got out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Got up from my barrack, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thought I have to go through this gate and to this-- to this other camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember a lot, but I don't remember how I did it, because I must've done it in a-- in a super-- in a-- in a state completely not human anymore, because it was definitely-- you know, if something would have gone wrong, I would have been shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I didn't think how I was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was just doing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So somehow, I did get to this camp with searchlight, with soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
